quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  23,105,"Koo, shimwasomelungwa ta tsinyali tsianje nanyu nimutsiyingasia?"
  23,106,"Baliboola mbu; “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, obubii bwefu bwakhuyinga muno, mana nikhuba abandu abakori."
  23,107,"Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khurusie mumulilo kuno (okhukalusie khushialo khukhole amalayi), ne nikhukalulishila khandi, khulaba ababii.""
  23,108,"Aliboola mbu; “Nyiremwo tsi! Ne mulalomalomia tawe.”"
  23,109,"Toto omukanda kwaliwo kwabasumba banje kwaboolanga mbu; “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khusuubile, kho khuleshele ebionono biefu ne okhubeele tsimbabaasi. Nawe newe Owetsimbabaasi okhushila boosi.”"
  23,110,"Mana nimubakholela amachayo, mana okhula shinga babakoyania okhunzitsulila, ne mwabatsekhanga."
  23,111,"Toto Esie ebarunjile inyanga yino khulwa okhwifwila khwabu. Toto abo nibo abalibura."
  23,112,"Aliboola mbu; “Mwekhala ebise biyela birie khushialo, khukhubala khwemika?”"
  23,113,"Baliboola mbu; “Khwekhalamwo inyanga ndala nohomba ebise muyinyanga, kho reba balia ababalanga.”"
  23,114,"Aliboola mbu; “Enywe shimwekhalamwo tawe halali ebise bititi butswa, toto mumanyangakhwo sa!"
  23,115,"Koo, muparanga mbu khwabaloonga eshikhaya butswa, ne mbu enywe shimulikalusibwa khwifwe tawe?"
  23,116,"Niwoluyali Nyasaye Omwami watoto, abulaho ulaamungwa khubwatoto halali Ye, Nyasaye weshisaala shiobwami shioluyali."
  23,117,"Ne ulia ulaamanga halala nende Nyasaye nyasaye wundi, ye abula eshifune okhukhola ario, ne toto okhubalilwa ebikhole bibie khuli khu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi. Ne toto abakhayi shibalibura tawe."
  23,118,"Ne boola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndeshela ne umbeele tsimbabaasi. Newe toto omulayi muno wababeeli, Owetsimbabaasi muno.""